    "Redundant information might be useless in the short term but highly useful in the long term as it increases the likelihood of preserving important information.qeios.com doi.org/10.32388/2RBRWN.4Entanglement is a concept from quantum physics indicating that information may disperse so as not to be limited by the speed of light.",
